title: Tuesday Post Show (11-01-22)
itunes:title: Tuesday Post Show (11-01-22)
description:
We start the post with a few lottery stories and how much you’d actually win if you hit the Powerball. A woman who gave birth while in a coma. Why only half of UFO sightings can be explained. A woman sniffs her husband’s dirty underwear to make sure he’s not cheating. Raymundo thinks Lunchbox’s acting career is a scam. We get into a breakdown of everyone’s prospective acting careers. Brett James is on the BobbyCast this week! Lunchbox has a personal “What’s Wrong with People” after an issue with a woman on a flight.

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
